# Test Scripts Location

Always create test scripts in the `archive/` folder. The archive folder is gitignored and contains:
- Test scripts (e.g. `archive/Test-*.ps1`, `archive/company-review-tests/`)
- One-off utilities and reference scripts

Do not create test scripts in the project root or other tracked directories.
